high_descs: Pick up the potato on the table.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave.
Heat up the potato and take it back out of the microwave.
Take a step to the left to find a grey bin on the floor.
Place the potato in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed potato inside a grey bin.

high_descs: Turn right, turn left, take a step, the turn right and walk to the table on the right.
Take the potato on the table.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside, close the door, and turn the microwave on. Remove the potato when it's done and close the door.
Turn left then turn right and walk to the trash can.
Put the potato in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato in the trash can.

high_descs: move over to the left side of the kitchen table you're facing
grab a potato off of the table
turn right and walk over to the microwave at the end of the room on the left
place the potato inside the microwave and cook it
turn left and walk over to the garbage at the end of the room on your right
place the potato inside of the garbage
anns.task_desc: place a cooked potato in the garbage
